column1: %    Department of Mechanical and Aerospace Engineering
%  "Mean velocity scaling for compressible wall turbulence with heat transfer"
%  Trettel, Andrew and Larsson, Johan, Physics of Fluids, 28, 026102 (2016),
%  ( 2)              y+: Wall-normal coordinate, scaled by viscous units
%  ( 3)            Y+tl: Wall-normal coordinate, transformed by the Trettel-Larsson transformation (semi-local scaling)
%  ( 6)              u+: Reynolds-averaged streamwise velocity, scaled by viscous units
%  ( 7)            U+vd: Reynolds-averaged streamwise velocity, transformed by the Van Driest transformation
%  ( 8)            U+vs: Reynolds-averaged streamwise velocity, transformed by the viscous sublayer transformation
%  ( 9)            U+tl: Reynolds-averaged streamwise velocity, transformed by the Trettel-Larsson transformation
%  (14)              mu: Viscosity function evaluated at the Reynolds-averaged temperature
